    "en": {
      "title": "Kandakadu incident: 4 Air Force personnel arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Welikanda police say that two army soldiers and two air force soldiers who served in the camp were arrested today (1) on suspicion of the suspicious death of an inmate at the Kandakadu rehabilitation camp in Polonnaruwa Welikanda.",
        "The detainees of the Kandakadu camp clashed with the Army in connection with the suspicious death of an inmate on the 29th of this month.",
        "The police also say that among the escaped inmates, a group of nearly 126 inmates are missing.",
        "The arrested suspects are to be produced in the Polonnaruwa Magistrate's Court tomorrow (2)."
      ],
